{"tid":1393620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[解放香港] 解放軍駐港部隊新宣傳片 廣東話叫「後果自負」","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:01:16.000Z","uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"65f8ef4b9259d3cb38698cf177a8fcb9c758fefc","tid":1393620,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"政府修訂《逃犯條例》引起的衝突愈演愈烈，解放軍會否介入備受關注。解放軍駐港部隊昨日於微博發布最新宣傳片，片段以「不忘初心，守護香江」為主題，全長約3分鐘，分為「反恐」、「維穩」、「防衛」、「同心」4大主題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jr6Y0wJo5Bk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Djr6Y0wJo5Bk&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl52qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=6cc655f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jr6Y0wJo5Bk</a><br />\n<br />\n在「反恐」部分，有新界的士出現於街道畫面；「維穩」部分，有解放軍以廣東話重覆叫喊「後果自負」，又有解放軍展示紅旗，旗上印有繁體字「警告  停止衝擊  否則使用用武力」及英文字，更在發射催淚彈、裝甲車移除路障、發射水炮壓制後，有全副武裝解放軍持盾向前推進，並出現拘捕示威者的畫面。影片尾段，有一些香港市民讚賞解放軍強大及有紀律等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1564624460_At-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1564624460_At-1280w.jpg&h=03cf17ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c49a6c4306d7584b976ed242880cc096fe20dc9","tid":1393620,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚驚呀.jpg"},{"pid":"0ab57ad7fa501a36f65fe6feec89c70ff16680c5","tid":1393620,"uid":41116,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXSedWi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXSedWi.png&h=571103d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c8c87c998ea8a4748194659e633f36646e91ed2","tid":1393620,"uid":68099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"2:36 同香港巿民打成一片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad62f55ef56e84a69f10b4e14b105fde48d834d","tid":1393620,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHqdMXC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHqdMXC.gif&h=f5c33198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8fdcdac54e6b8afb26609da5b11316c0718fe66","tid":1393620,"uid":22622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ad62f55ef56e84a69f10b4e14b105fde48d834d","tid":1393620,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHqdMXC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHqdMXC.gif&h=f5c33198&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"嘩！隻角摺到咁尖，吉到一定好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7291e0b3217cf921e695ef713cf2ba3c0d3461","tid":1393620,"uid":21255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owWZp4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowWZp4w.png&h=c41e4729&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e93aa609dd2ec10309d97da68154661a77e367f","tid":1393620,"uid":262784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"黎喇黎喇<br />\n<br />\n好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ad115440c6001b62e5130a64b11ae3ee5929c9","tid":1393620,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:11:24.000Z","msg":"人哋國務院唔俾你班撚樣出呀<br />\n又要被連登仔恥笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dcbc849629c4ca5d675c1e551dd2f4c0d9ddfe","tid":1393620,"uid":262253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score